# No build-time configuration is required for the glasses app.
#
# The backend URL and auth token are entered at first launch through the
# in-app setup screen (displayed in the Even Hub phone companion app).
# They are stored in the WebView's localStorage so the app remembers them
# across sessions without a rebuild.
#
# If you need to pre-configure during development you can still create
# .env.local and set VITE_BACKEND_URL_OVERRIDE=ws://192.168.x.x:8787
# then read it in main.ts — but this is not required for normal use.
